data.description: IF YOU ARE NEEDING TO BE CLOSE TO THE UNIVERSITY OF SOUTH ALABAMA, THIS IS THE HOME FOR YOU! CONVENIENTLY LOCATED IN THE UNIVERSITY PARK NEIGHBORHOOD. LOVELY HOME THAT HAS LOTS OF UPGRADES; NEW PAINT THROUGHOUT, LIGHTS, NEW TILED PRIMARY SHOWER, NEW SLIDING GLASS DOOR IN THE LIVING ROOM, AND BRAND NEW A/C UNIT! THE KITCHEN AND LIVING ROOM/DINING ROOM ARE ON THE MAIN LEVEL, UPSTAIRS YOU WILL FIND THE PRIMARY BEDROOM, 2 ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS AND 2 FULL BATHS. DOWNSTAIRS IS A LARGE DEN WITH BUILT INS, HALF BATH AND THE LAUNDRY ROOM. FENCED BACK YARD! SQUARE FOOTAGE INCLUDES A 422 SF DEN DOWNSTAIRS.  MAKE YOUR APPOINTMENT TODAY!  All information provided is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer or buyer’s agent to verify all information.
